snippet.title: BATTLE JUNK // Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2448780/BATTLE_JUNK/

This game is a 3D bullet hell action game. You can possess enemy characters and switch them with your own. Featuring 3D graphics with a pixel art aesthetic!

Developed by
haraha
